Load an endpoint by alias

Source: R/endpoint.R
endpoint.Rd

Load an endpoint by alias

Usage

endpoint(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

Value

An S7 <class_care/caid/prov/open/hgov> object.

Examples
